Put the radishes in a bowl.Put the lime juice (reserving 2 tablespoons), sugar, red onion, oil and dill in a smaller bowl. Stir, then pour onto the radishes and mix gently. This only needs 10 minutes to infuse.Meanwhile, toast the bread.Mash the avocados with the reserved 2 tablespoons of lime juice to prevent any browning. Spread the toast with the avocados and add a sprinkling of black pepper.Drain the radishes and onions through a colander to remove any excess lime juice, then arrange them on top of the avocado to serve.